Shadownav

What the project is for
	-Responsive Bootstrap 3.3.7 navbar shadow effects
	-Works with default navbar, navbar static top and navbar fixed top styles
	
How to configure and install it
	1. Add link to shadownav.css after bootstrap CSS files
	2. Wrap nav element with a div containing the appropriate shadownav wrapper class
		-.sn-default-wrapper for (default) navbar
		-.sn-static-wrapper for static-top-navbar
		-.sn-fixed-wrapper for static-fixed-navbar
	3. Wrap dropdown-menu anchors' text with divs (for correct dropdown menu inset shadow optics and link functionality)
	4. For animations
		-Add link to jquery ui after jquery (for jquery ui slide effect)
		-Assign jq-anim or jq-ui-anim (for jquery ui slide effect) class to shadownav wrapper assigned div
		-Add script after bootstrap JS files
		
An example of how to use it or get it running
	Extract files for example/examples
	
