Getting Started
Extract files for example
or
To use plugin with default bootstrap navbar (https://getbootstrap.com/docs/3.3/examples/navbar/)
	1. Link to shadownav.css after navbar.css in head
	2. Wrap nav with shadownav-wrapper
	3. Wrap anchors' text with divs

Prerequisites
Everything is included

